    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i run a small cafe in a rural town where stuff is pretty cheap. i'm hearing a lot of talk about raising the minimum wage again. how do these kinds of changes usually impact small businesses in places like mine?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
